(35, 1, '2015-04-27 00:06:47', '2015-04-26 21:06:47', '<a href=\"http://savemari.co.tz/wp-content/uploads/2015/04/how-to-post-an-ad.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone size-large wp-image-36\" src=\"http://savemari.co.tz/wp-content/uploads/2015/04/how-to-post-an-ad-500x143.jpg\" alt=\"how-to-post-an-ad\" width=\"500\" height=\"143\" /></a>\r\n<h2></h2>\r\n<h2>Here is how to post a new ad!</h2>\r\n<ol>\r\n	<li>On the savemari.co.tz homepage, click on the “Post an Ad” button to the right of the main navigation menu. This will take you to Step 1, where you select the relevant category to which your ad belongs to. Click “Go” to proceed.</li>\r\n	<li>Continuing on Step 1, complete the relevant fields on the ad form. If the “Featured Listing” check box is available, you can select this to have your ad appear in the featured ads slider. Depending on the price structure set for the site, you may see a dropdown box containing Ad Package options, and a “Coupon Code” field which will allow you to use a discount coupon offered by the site. Click “Continue” to proceed.</li>\r\n	<li>Step 2 allows you to review your listing, and the summary of how much the ad will cost. If it is a paid ad, then you will see a dropdown menu with the payment gateway options available.</li>\r\n	<li>Step 3. You will see one of the following options:If the ad is free, you will receive a success message and an indication of whether or not the ad is live or pending review</li>\r\n	<li>If it is a paid ad using the PayPal payment gateway you will be redirected to PayPal to complete your transaction. At the end of that process you will see a link back to the classifieds site to review your ad which is published immediately after payment has been made.</li>\r\n	<li>If it is a paid ad using the bank transfer option, you will see a screen containing your unique ad details and bank transfer instructions. In the case of these ads, the ad remains pending until the site admin manually approves the ad after also manually confirming the payment has been received.</li>\r\n</ol>\r\nWe hope this has been helpful. Drop us an <a title=\"Contact Us\" href=\"http://savemari.com/contact-us/\">email</a> or visit our facebook page: <a title=\"Savemari.com\" href=\"http://www.facebook.com/Savemari\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.facebook.com/Savemari</a> to let us know.\r\n\r\n<strong>Savemari.com support.</strong>', 'How To Post An Ad on Savemari.co.tz', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'how-to-post-an-ad-on-savemari-co-tz', '', '', '2015-04-27 00:08:10', '2015-04-26 21:08:10', 'How To Post An Ad on Savemari.co.tz, Here is how to post a new ad! On the savemari.co.tz homepage, click on the “Post an Ad” button to the right of the main navigation menu. This will take you to Step 1, where you select the relevant category to which your ad belongs to. Click “Go” to proceed. Continuing on Step 1, complete the relevant fields on the ad form. If the “Featured Listing” check box is available, you can select this to have your ad appear in the featured ads slider. Depending on the price structure set for the site, you may see a dropdown box containing Ad Package options, and a “Coupon Code” field which will allow you to use a discount coupon offered by the site. Click “Continue” to proceed. Step 2 allows you to review your listing, and the summary of how much the ad will cost. If it is a paid ad, then you will see a dropdown menu with the payment gateway options available. Step 3. You will see one of the following options:If the ad is free, you will receive a success message and an indication of whether or not the ad is live or pending review If it is a paid ad using the PayPal payment gateway you will be redirected to PayPal to complete your transaction. At the end of that process you will see a link back to the classifieds site to review your ad which is published immediately after payment has been made. If it is a paid ad using the bank transfer option, you will see a screen containing your unique ad details and bank transfer instructions. In the case of these ads, the ad remains pending until the site admin manually approves the ad after also manually confirming the payment has been received. We hope this has been helpful. Drop us an email or visit our facebook page: http://www.facebook.com/Savemari to let us know. Savemari.com support., Uncategorized', 0, 'http://savemari.co.tz/?p=35', 0, 'post', '', 0),
