(285, 8, '2016-01-18 19:15:58', '2016-01-18 16:15:58', '<div id=\"tabinfo-care-info\" class=\"tab-content\">\r\n<h2>Product information</h2>\r\nIntroduce a whole new level of style to your kitchen with the Samsung RF24FSEDBSR 4-door fridge freezer.\r\n\r\nAdvanced style and flexibility make this French door freezer the ultimate cooling statement. With a stylish stainless steel finish, this uniquely designed fridge freezer hosts a giant 510 litres of storage space.\r\n\r\nThis fridge freezer hosts a standard opening top section with 5 fridge shelves and 2 salad drawers, providing optimal humidity levels to preserve the taste and nutrients in your fruits and vegetables. An Easy Access Mid Drawer with independent temperature control aids flexibility and convenience. Select from 4 different temperatures whether you want to store cold drinks, deli items, meat and fish or even wine at the optimum temperature. The Smart Divider also allows for added customisation of your storage space to suit the whole family\'s needs. Two easy-slide freezer drawers complete the configuration of this model.\r\n\r\nTwin Cooling Plus provides optimal humidity to keep food fresher for longer and prevents any transfer of odours between the fridge and freezer compartments. Thin wall insulation technology allows you to store more food and drink and organise your groceries more easily. Thanks to the water and ice dispenser, which requires plumbing in to your water supply, you can enjoy continuous filtered water and crushed or cubed ice at the touch of a button.\r\n\r\nVersatile shelving options let you store oversized items with ease, and with the addition of MultiFlow cooling vents on every shelf your food is always stored in an even and stable environment. Extra storage space is also on hand in the left door guard.\r\n\r\nYou’ll always be able to spot that last bit of food with the bright LED lights illuminating every corner. Full no-frost technology tops off this model and means never having to worry about icy build-ups or defrosting your refrigerator again.\r\n\r\n<strong>Dimensions: H177.7 x W90.8 x D78.8 cm (depth includes handles)</strong>\r\n\r\n<dl><dt>24 Hour Freezing Capacity <a class=\"info tooltip-trigger\" href=\"http://www.johnlewis.com/samsung-rf24fsedbsr-4-door-fridge-freezer-stainless-steel/p469234?sku=232124890&amp;kpid=232124890&amp;s_kenid=620a175d-851e-40b2-b9e0-25caca4c32ff&amp;s_kwcid=402x354299&amp;tmad=c&amp;tmcampid=73#tooltip\">Information</a></dt><dd>6kg</dd></dl><dl><dt>Antibacterial protection <a class=\"info tooltip-trigger\" href=\"http://www.johnlewis.com/samsung-rf24fsedbsr-4-door-fridge-freezer-stainless-steel/p469234?sku=232124890&amp;kpid=232124890&amp;s_kenid=620a175d-851e-40b2-b9e0-25caca4c32ff&amp;s_kwcid=402x354299&amp;tmad=c&amp;tmcampid=73#tooltip\">Information</a></dt><dd>YES</dd></dl><dl><dt>Average annual energy cost <a class=\"info tooltip-trigger\" href=\"http://www.johnlewis.com/samsung-rf24fsedbsr-4-door-fridge-freezer-stainless-steel/p469234?sku=232124890&amp;kpid=232124890&amp;s_kenid=620a175d-851e-40b2-b9e0-25caca4c32ff&amp;s_kwcid=402x354299&amp;tmad=c&amp;tmcampid=73#tooltip\">Information</a></dt><dd>£42.70</dd></dl><dl><dt>Brand</dt><dd>\r\n<div>Samsung</div>\r\n</dd></dl><dl><dt>Dimensions</dt><dd>H177.7 x W90.8 x D78.8 cm</dd></dl><dl><dt>Eligible for International Delivery</dt><dd>NO</dd></dl><dl><dt>Energy Consumption Per Standard Cycle <a class=\"info tooltip-trigger\" href=\"http://www.johnlewis.com/samsung-rf24fsedbsr-4-door-fridge-freezer-stainless-steel/p469234?sku=232124890&amp;kpid=232124890&amp;s_kenid=620a175d-851e-40b2-b9e0-25caca4c32ff&amp;s_kwcid=402x354299&amp;tmad=c&amp;tmcampid=73#tooltip\">Information</a></dt><dd>427kWh/year</dd></dl><dl><dt>Energy Rating <a class=\"info tooltip-trigger\" href=\"http://www.johnlewis.com/samsung-rf24fsedbsr-4-door-fridge-freezer-stainless-steel/p469234?sku=232124890&amp;kpid=232124890&amp;s_kenid=620a175d-851e-40b2-b9e0-25caca4c32ff&amp;s_kwcid=402x