(687, 35, 'description', 'RE: INTRODUCTION TO EAC LOGISTICS SOLUTIONS LTD\r\n\r\nPreamble:\r\nEAC Logistics Solutions Ltd is a Tanzanian registered company whose primary business is to plan, design, implement and manage a wide spectrum of logistics requirement for diverse clients. We focus on finding the best transportation mode for goods, from exports, imports, local to regional distribution. Additionally, it also offers customs clearance, logistic consultancy &amp; support to organizations and individuals within and outside Tanzania by linking them to a network of partner agents both locally and globally. \r\n\r\nEAC Logistics Solutions Ltd is currently servicing clients with shipment via Sea (through ports of Mombasa, Tanga and/or Dar es Salaam) or via Air (through Kilimanjaro, Dar es Salaam or Nairobi airports). The service is offered with collaboration with contracted suppliers, airlines, shipping lines, transporters and partner agents to achieve maximum optimization level in terms of both time and cost. EAC Logistics will work with key industry players and regulatory authorities to create a smooth operation experience for its customers.  \r\n\r\nServices offered:\r\nIn brief, we offer the following services:-\r\n•	Air &amp; Sea Freight forwarding\r\n•	Customs Clearing of import &amp; export\r\n•	Airline Cargo Booking- representatives of major airlines\r\n•	Border Clearance &amp; Facilitation\r\n•	Road Transport\r\n•	Warehousing &amp; Distribution\r\n•	Logistics Support &amp; Consultancy\r\n•	Commissions Agents\r\n•	Representative for various Global Forwarders\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\nPortfolio:\r\nSome of our major clients in Tanzania are:-\r\n•	Darsh Industries Ltd (REDGOLD)\r\n•	Off Grid Electric (T) Ltd (Mpower)\r\n•	OSHO Chemicals Ltd\r\n•	Shamba Technologies Ltd\r\n•	Karibu Solar Power Ltd\r\n•	Jobex Financial Services Ltd\r\n•	Laangi Gems Ltd\r\n•	Genesis Logistics Ltd\r\n•	Sierra Ltd\r\n•	Ongeza Tanzania Ltd\r\n\r\nCompetencies:\r\nWe listen to understand your business operating requirement and suggest workable solutions so that your shipments are delivered at shortest time possible. We understand the bottlenecks along the supply chain thus plan ahead to mitigate them so your business is not adversely affected by delays or suffer unnecessary escalation of costs. We are ready to engage your team to plan early for smooth operations; as well as react quickly to any adhoc requests that may arise. Our experience has given us excellent operational competencies at Dar es Salaam, Mombasa and Tanga Sea ports as well as the airports at Dar es salaam &amp; Kilimanjaro major border point across busy road freight routes. We are confident that your company will benefit from our current &amp; relevant market relationships. Besides, our regional reach will enable you to deal with a single office for your regional logistics requirements and thus improving efficiency. \r\n\r\nEAC Logistics Advantage:\r\n	Largest Solar Industry Equipment Logistics provider in Tanzania, so we know all the ropes\r\n	Single Customs Territory (SCT) know-how – delivers anywhere in East Africa\r\n	Efficient Operations at Mombasa, Dar es salaam, Kilimanjaro &amp; Border points – Localized to your convenience.  \r\n	Adaptive and proactive staff ready to work with you throughout the shipment cycle\r\n	Lean management structure for prompt decisions – no Red tape! \r\n\r\nOur Partners:\r\nEAC Logistics Solutions Ltd is associated with WAFEM TZ Ltd (TZ), Nibal Freighters Ltd (KE), JM Freight (UG) and Royal Link (RW) all in a wider Logistic Group and together are able to deliver a seamless services at all customs entry points within East Africa Community states. EAC Logistics Group is soon launching in DRC and South Sudan.  \r\n\r\n\r\nKey Contacts (Tanzania):- \r\n\r\nMr. Daniel Mugo\r\nManaging Director\r\nTel. +255 787 416612 | +254724383015\r\nEmail: admin@eaclogistics.com |Skype: fitmugo\r\n\r\nDar es Salaam Office:\r\nJames Mramba\r\nBusiness Dev. Manager\r\nBenjamin William Mkapa House\r\nParking Tower, Ground floor, Jamhuri Street\r\nP.O BOX 78417, Dar es Salaam Tanzania.\r\nTel: +255 738 282 172 | Mobile: +255 787 611511\r\nEmail: james@eaclogistics.com\r\n\r\nArusha Office:\r\nMr. Genes Raymond Maunga\r\nFinance Director\r\n1st Flr Suite 219, New Safari Hotel-Business wing, India Street.\r\nP.O Box 16549 Arusha, Tanzania\r\nTel: +255 272 545363 | Mobile: +255 782 398636\r\nEmail: genes@eaclogistics.com\r\n\r\nIn Conclusion: \r\nWe are confident in building a lasting business relationship with you. Please feel free to engage the undersigned should you require further clarification as well as a request of our standard rates. Many thanks! \r\n\r\nWarm Regards,\r\n\r\nk.mremi		\r\n\r\nkelvin mremi\r\nSales Executive'),
